th_text_P6j4pJ":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_x9LaHi":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_cPmjA8":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h2><strong>What is an Electric Tricycle?<\/strong><\/h2><p><\/p><p>An <a href=\"\/collections\/trike\" title=\"e-Trikes\">electric tricycle<\/a> is a short-distance transportation vehicle featuring a three-wheel design and powered by an electric motor. Its core function is electric-assisted propulsion. With a stable structural design and versatile practical features, it precisely meets the daily commuting and shopping needs of diverse users. Combining effort-saving, safety, convenience, and eco-friendliness, it stands as an excellent choice for everyday travel.<\/p><h2><strong>Why Choose Electric Tricycles<\/strong><\/h2><h2><\/h2><p>At its core, the competitive edge of <a href=\"\/collections\/trike\" title=\"e-Trikes\">electric tricycles<\/a> lies in the dual assurances of “effort-saving” and “safety.” Its electric motor provides steady power assistance, significantly reducing physical exertion during riding. Whether for individuals with limited stamina or for extended short-distance trips, it handles effortlessly, eliminating the strenuous challenges of traditional cycling. Unlike two-wheeled vehicles, its three-wheel design ensures exceptional stability, effectively mitigating the risk of tipping during turns or on bumpy roads, making it safe for users of all ages.<br\/><\/p>","text_style":"subtitle"}}},"block_order":["heading_x9LaHi","text_cPmjA8"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/mf30-outdoor-1.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}}},"order":["banner","product-g